      "updated": 1776328585338,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Multiple queries\n\nLinear search  =  TC = O(N*Q)\n\nBinary search = TC = O(Q*log(n))\n\nMap = TC = O(Q+N) => O(N)",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Multiple queries\n\nLinear search  =  TC = O(N*Q)\n\nBinary search = TC = O(Q*log(n))\n\nMap = TC = O(Q+N) => O(N)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
